00:11:33.010 --> 00:11:38.139
You can truly appreciate depth and the scale
of the mountain ranges; Pluto almost seems

00:11:38.139 --> 00:11:44.509
like a toy replica due to the extreme topographical
relief, but these mountains appear so high

00:11:44.509 --> 00:11:49.319
because Pluto is so small, and its gravity
is not strong enough to pull them down.

00:11:49.319 --> 00:11:58.050
This gives for a varied and impressive landscape
and a fitting end to the video.

